# LLM Wiki Vault (Cursor specifics)

The full operating contract lives in `AGENTS.md` at the vault root — read and
follow it (session start: read `wiki/hot.md` silently; re-read after context
compaction).

Cursor-specific carve-outs:

- The project hook `.cursor/hooks/wiki-autocommit.sh` auto-commits `wiki/`,
  `.raw/`, `.vault-meta/` after file edits. This is user-sanctioned automation
  and an explicit exception to any global ask-before-commit rule — do not
  fight it or warn about it. Ask-before-commit still applies to every other
  path and to commits you make yourself.
- The `stop` hook may prompt you to refresh `wiki/hot.md` if wiki pages
  changed; comply using the hot-cache format in `AGENTS.md`.
